title: The Nazi Black Book
description: The Nazi black book, a list of those to be arrested and dealt with if Germany occupied Britain, privation in wartime and Allied-occupied Austria, racial tension in 1940s Sweden, plus how Britain's Labour party moved against hereditary peers in the House of Lords in the 1990s.
itunes:subtitle: The Nazi arrest list for Britain, wartime Austria, and anti-traveller riots in Sweden
